rulesList.cssText: body { background: white; color: black; font-family: sans-serif; line-height: 1.4em; text-align: center; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; }
#banner { background: black; color: rgb(242, 242, 242); line-height: 1.2em; padding: 0.3em 1em; box-shadow: black 0px 5px 10px; }
#main { text-align: left; margin: 0px auto; min-width: 32em; max-width: 66em; }
#menu { float: right; width: 13em; padding: 0px; border-left: 2px solid rgb(221, 221, 221); }
.nav ul li { list-style-type: none; padding: 0px; margin: 0px; }
h1 { display: block; font-size: 3em; text-align: left; margin: 0.5rem 0px 0px; }
h2 { font-size: 2rem; line-height: 2.25rem; margin: 1rem 0px 0.5rem; overflow-wrap: break-word; }
table.news .date { text-align: right; padding: 0.75rem 0.5rem 0px 0px; white-space: nowrap; }
.dropbtn { background-color: rgb(128, 128, 128); color: white; padding: 0.3rem; font-size: 1rem; border: 1px solid rgb(96, 96, 96); }
.dropdown-content { display: none; position: absolute; background-color: rgb(240, 240, 240); min-width: 160px; box-shadow: rgb(144, 144, 144) 0px 8px 12px 0px; z-index: 1; }
.dropdown-content a { padding: 0.33em; text-decoration: none; display: block; }
div.directive { background: rgb(242, 242, 242); line-height: 1em; margin: 1em 0px 1em -1em; padding: 0.7em 0.7em 0.7em 1em; border-top: 2px solid rgb(221, 221, 221); width: 100%; }
div.directive th { padding-left: 0px; padding-right: 0.5em; vertical-align: baseline; text-align: left; font-weight: normal; }
div.directive code { border: none; background: none !important; padding: 0px !important; }
blockquote.note { padding: 0.5rem; border: 1px dotted rgb(153, 153, 153); line-height: 1.2em; text-align: justify; }
pre { border: 0px; display: block; margin: 1em 0px; padding: 0.6em 1em; overflow-x: auto; line-height: 1.05rem; }
code, .legacy { font-size: 100%; padding: 3px 7px; overflow-x: scroll; background: rgb(238, 238, 238); }
pre code { background: none; padding: 0px; border-radius: 0px; }
blockquote pre { margin: 0px; border: 1px solid rgb(221, 221, 221); background-color: rgb(248, 248, 248) !important; color: rgb(34, 34, 34) !important; }
blockquote.terminal pre { background-color: rgb(68, 68, 68) !important; color: rgb(255, 255, 255) !important; }
.video iframe, .video object, .video embed { position: absolute; top: 0px; left: 0px; width: 100%; height: 100%; }

.nav { width: 15rem; height: 100%; max-height: 0px; position: fixed; top: 50px; right: 0px; border-left: 1px solid rgb(144, 144, 144); background-color: var(--white); overflow: hidden; transition: 0.5s ease-in-out; }
.nav ul li { list-style-type: none; padding: 0px; margin: 0px; }
.hamb { cursor: pointer; float: right; position: absolute; top: 0px; right: 0.25em; width: 3.5em; padding-top: 1.5em; z-index: 1100; }
.hamb-line { background: var(--green); display: block; position: relative; height: 0.3em; width: 2.75em; border-radius: 3px; }
.hamb-line::before, .hamb-line::after { background: var(--green); content: ""; display: block; height: 100%; position: absolute; transition: 0.2s ease-in-out; width: 100%; border-radius: 3px; }
blockquote pre { border: 1px solid rgb(19, 34, 53); color: rgb(221, 221, 221) !important; background: rgb(15, 27, 41) !important; }
div.directive { background: rgb(12, 22, 34) !important; border-top: 2px solid rgb(32, 60, 94) !important; }
